node.text: Took a trip to Manchester, UK to model for one of my favorite brands. A small snippet of a training session at 4am, had jet lag so I couldn’t sleep. New @becomenutrition Tee 🙏🏾⚡️

Become “Focus” Tee: I wanted to capture the raw level of focus it takes me to be what I am. This pic was taken in my gym, in 100 degree weather, after a few sleepless nights, mid-training. You can see the damn bags under my eyes in the tee. I want you to rock this & be motivated to approach your game, whatever it may be, with a game face. A game face is the only way to face your game, Become. #BeFocused #BecomeNutrition 

Link in bio here: @becomenutrition

node.text:
That’s a wrap for Double Cross szn III 🎬

Been filming all month out here in LA. S/o to our crew, every department, our directors, writer & all the loyal @doublecrossseries viewers! Much love 

Been living in a hotel / random gyms this entire time. Missing the fam like crazy. There’s more projects I’m hyped about birthing when I get back. 

There’s more work to do. Expect more. Become more.
